channel.title: How do you get servers online?
channel.description:
I've been trying to get my PimpScape server online. NOW, I can get online on it, but no one else can...
It says 'Error connecting to server. Must be down. Click start server to create your own.'
I've tried basically everything to get this thing running but nothing's worked so far...
Anyone got a solution as to how I can get this piece of crap running?
NOTE: I don't have Hamachi.
